Name: Average resolution time for incidents marked as \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Median time from \Accepted + In Progress\ to \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Difference in average resolution time between \Completed + Resolved\ and \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time spent in \Accepted + Wait - User\ before reaching \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Longest time from \Accepted + Assigned\ to \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Shortest time from \Accepted + Wait - Implementation\ to \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time incidents spend in \Accepted + Wait - Vendor\ before \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total resolution time for \Completed + Closed\ incidents in the VINST system
Metric: The sum of the duration between the beginning of the case and activity 'Completed + Closed' for cases where activity 'Completed + Closed' occurs

Name: Average delay time for \Completed + Closed\ due to \Accepted + Wait - Customer\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average elapsed time between \Completed + In Call\ and \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Comparison of resolution times from \Accepted + Wait\ to \Completed + Closed\ versus \Accepted + Wait - User\ to \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Cycle time analysis for incidents from \Queued + Awaiting Assignment\ to \Completed + Closed\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Detailed time analysis from first activity to \Completed + Closed\ for high-frequency process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum, maximum, and average time from \Accepted + Wait - Implementation\ to \Completed + Closed\ for critical incidents
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
